// quickref

QuickRef is a timer-based drawing reference tool for gesture drawing and sketching. Use it to do long form timed practice, warm up sessions, or focused gesture practice. Unlike other similar tools, QuickRef is specifically designed for using your own reference images on your computer.


No static libraries, no mandatory subscription, no internet connection.

// moodial timer

Moondial timer is a tiny stopwatch, chronometer, and countdown timer library with support for millisecond precision built in TypeScript. Originally built as part of QuickRef, moondial provides high precision event-based clocks with a simple API.
